The immediate area offers a wide variety of shops, supermarkets, and specialty stores for your daily needs. In addition, there is an abundance of charming cafés and restaurants nearby. For a good cup of coffee or lunch, you can visit Bagels & Beans or one of the many popular local hotspots.

