The bathroom is functionally designed and fitted with a shower, washbasin, and toilet. The practical layout provides everything needed for everyday comfort.

The apartment also benefits from a balcony, where you can enjoy the fresh air and views of the surrounding greenery. It is a wonderful place to start or end the day.

